me":"2020-07-11T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"掉落垃圾桶<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>為什麽不回收即棄電池？<br />\n <br />\n回收即棄電池的經濟及環境效益遠不及回收充電池。原因如下：<br />\n回收即棄電池的成本遠高於充電池，而且，在循環再造中可提取的小量鐵、鋅及錳的價值亦不高。此外，即棄電池的回收再造設施主要位於歐洲和美國，運費會令成本增加。<br />\n<br />\n香港已有完善設施可以安全地處置電池。我們在堆填區鋪設不滲漏層，廢物的滲漏液會經收集和處理後，才排放入污水渠。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/workplace/rechargebattery_faq.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wastereduction.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fworkplace%2Frechargebattery_faq.htm&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=a1008ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wastereduction.gov.hk/tc/workplace/rechargebattery_faq.htm</a>"},{"pid":"70352579b68d322da0fabfb1a85532116f0b3d6e","tid":2103795,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"掉垃圾桶"},{"pid":"b35b2a6da75c8c7384da491c10f88abf2e85d1ac","tid":2103795,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"直接掉落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3e9f55a6cda786a8c79ae28de377311423eecb","tid":2103795,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"港鐵站有電池回收箱"},{"pid":"cd9a298fdec304a8f890bdbafa0e9e96862ab064","tid":2103795,"uid":123988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"其實呢個世界應該禁左即棄電池<br />\n因為即棄電真係好垃圾<br />\n電得少少<br />\n但垃圾就永恆。。又污染"},{"pid":"36742657362599a08811b49814c4b34a4de36cff","tid":2103795,"uid":57166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c3e9f55a6cda786a8c79ae28de377311423eecb","tid":2103795,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"港鐵站有電池回收箱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"收充電果D?"},{"pid":"3dad84d1376ac626996a043809c678e98095f3d5","tid":2103795,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"